(****************************************************)
(*              R is complete :                     *)
(*        Each sequence which satisfies             *)
(*       the Cauchy's criterion converges           *)
(*                                                  *)
(*    Proof with adjacent sequences (Vn and Wn)     *)
(****************************************************)


forall Un : nat -> R,
Cauchy_crit Un -> {l : R | Un_cv Un l}
